org.openpsa.notifications Changelog
                   -----------------------------------
Legend:
- All items marked with "!" represent a major API-Change that is
  not guaranteed to be backwards compatible to previous versions
  which might even break existing functionality.
- All items marked with "+" represent completely new features.

2009-06-23 xfade
  - removed user spoofing
  - added default sender config option

2007-02-09 bergie
  + Initial support for sending notifications via a Nabaztag WiFi bunny
  + Implemented component-shipped default values for notifications
  + Implemented a notification preferences plugin for net.nehmer.account

2006-10-27 rambo
  + attachments support to email notifications
  - minor bulletproofing (no empty subject, dump array if no content not defined)
  - version bump

2006-09-14 bergie
  + Created org_openpsa_notifications_notification object for stored
    notifications

2006-05-24 bergie
  + Initial version supporting only calendar events and emails